text: Chilimny () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Kilinchinsky Selsoviet, Privolzhsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 46 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 25 km from Astrakhan, 18 km from Nachalovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Privolzhsky District, Astrakhan Oblast
title: Chilimny
